Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:46.26,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(400,400)}凝结千言万语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.96,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(400,400)}那么简单的一句话
